column2: SELECT TOP # a.OBJID AS OBJID, a.RA AS RA, a.DEC AS DEC, /* sp.z AS zsp, sp.zErr AS e_zsp, sp.class AS class, sp.subClass AS subClass, sp.zWarning AS zWarning, sp.mode AS mode, */ /* PhotoObjAll */ ph.objID AS sdssid, ph.ra AS RA_sdss, ph.dec AS DEC_sdss, ph.mode AS mode, ph.probPSF AS probPSF, /* propability that object is the star */ ph.modelMag_u AS umag, ph.modelMag_g AS gmag, ph.modelMag_r AS rmag, ph.modelMag_i AS imag, ph.modelMag_z AS zmag, ph.modelMagErr_u AS e_umag, ph.modelMagErr_g AS e_gmag, ph.modelMagErr_r AS e_rmag, ph.modelMagErr_i AS e_imag, ph.modelMagErr_z AS e_zmag, n.distance AS angDist from MyDB.akari AS a CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (a.RA, a.RA, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll as ph ON n.objid = ph.objid /* JOIN */ where a.OBJID < #
